tags.name: rss-items
tags.description:
`rss-items`
`visualize RSS items`

Example:
```html
<rss-items
  url="https://content.therapychat.com/rss.xml"
  max="4"
  auto
></rss-items>
```
It will retrieve the items from the url automatically.
tags.jsDoc:

  ```
 * It will retrieve the items from the url automatically.

 */
